text:
Aunty is friendly and they sell snacks and ice cream ( at least that’s what I buy )
I bought ice cream and it taste good
10/10

Always come here to collect my shoppee packages. This store is great because you can get many food/drink items cheap, more worth to get from here than commercial areas and super convenient under HDB block near bishan park~

Store faces Bishan Park. Seems to have standard products for a convenience store.
I was there to collect items that I ordered from Lazada.
I always go there after my weekend jog. Service is good and staff is friendly. Would definitely recommend this place if you don’t mind the children there being rowdy and obnoxious
Friendly staff even though im there to dropoff parcels. Will buy stuff from there next time.
